      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great",
          "reviewText": "absolutely love the L\u2019Or\u00e9al Paris True Match Foundation! This has quickly become my go-to foundation. The shade match is seriously impressive \u2014 it blends so seamlessly into my skin that it actually looks like my skin, just smoother and more even. The formula feels lightweight and breathable, not cakey or heavy at all. It gives such a natural, radiant finish while still providing great coverage for redness and blemishes. I also appreciate that it layers beautifully without looking patchy. For the price, the quality is amazing. It performs like a high-end foundation but is super affordable. I\u2019ve worn it for long days and it holds up really well without separating or settling into fine lines. Definitely a 5-star product \u2014 I will be repurchasing!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 27, 2026",
