        {
          "reviewTitle": "Decent product for the price",
          "reviewText": "Not bad! Definitely is blendable but very runny and feels a bit greasy by the end of the day. I am not an oily person, so this isn't common for me. It isn't sticky, the color match was a bit lighter than I expected but it worked fine for winter. No scent to it. Overall, decent product for the price! It's easy to apply and blend, you just have to be fast because it is drippy and I would say that more comes out per pump than you'd expect.",
